articles.title: ’SPECTACULAR!’ Why you can’t argue if Messi wins the Ballon d'Or ahead of Haaland | ESPN FC - ESPN UK
articles.description: ESPN FC’s Janusz Michallik joins Mark Donaldson to react to Pep Guardiola’s comments about Lionel Messi and Erling Haaland both winning the Ballon d'Or.Subsc...
